{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Scaredy Cat</strong> is a pixel mystery  adventure title that begins with a familiar tale.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Henny</strong> has been worn to the bone by a soul-sucking corporate career that has gifted her with heart problems. Swept up in a rare glimpse of emotion, she rage quits and starts pet sitting. Little does she know, her new gig will be just as horrifying as her last.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919030/extras/story.png?t=1733525614\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A lovingly crafted and emotional narrative with a deeper message</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A perfect mesh of beloved 2D pixel graphics and narrative-as-a-pillar</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Deep, well-developed characters that you can learn about at your own pace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore the city of Conhaven and its surroundings - beautiful pixel environments that eradiate spook and atmosphere</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919030/extras/2.png?t=1733525614\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Select Pet Sitting Gigs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Solve environmental and cognitive puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Care for critters and encounter supernatural horrors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Discover touching stories about pet owners</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Progress through gigs to uncover a more sinister plot and become a more brave and purposeful Henny</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass